# Corbind
- Corbind presents itself as a complete, 100% integrated book ecosystem for readers, writers, and digital influencers, offering all the features they desire without intermediaries. It guarantees autonomy, freedom, and empowerment for writers, while keeping content free and considering the habits of new generations, innovating in the way books are written and consumed.

## Products
- Publish books on chain
- Read books by rent (pay per page read)
- Royalties distribution
- Ads (e.g. promote a book)

## Mission
- Democratize and decentralize the industry, empowering people with autonomy and full freedom to transform their lives through books.
- Connect people and create memories, with books and their stories at the center.
- Make books a part of everyone's daily life through innovation in production and consumption methods for modern and future times.

## Vision
- To be the largest book ecosystem.
- To be the most spontaneous response from everyone when the subject is books.
- To lead the new era of the decentralized economy, connecting people to opportunities with more freedom.

## Values
- Human: Made for and with people; for all our perfect imperfections.
- Universal: For everyone. For every moment. Regardless of time and taste, you'll find it at Corbind.
- Mutual: Everyone wins, without harming or competing with each other.
- Freedom: Everything I need is within my reach, in a simple and easy way.
- Integral: Everything I need is in one place, but at the same time it's not confusing.

## Target Audience
- Publisher (tradicional, digital or independent)
- Readers: woman between 15 and 45 years old
- writers: (independent)
- São Paulo, Brazil
- Web3 enthusiasts and investors

